WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:11.380
Cut the French bread into slices

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:30.900
Mix the grated cheese into the mayonnaise

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:47.180
spread suitable amounts onto the French bread slices.

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:55.680
Bake in a 180-degree preheated oven for about 7 minutes until golden brown

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:11.840
Take it out and spread the mentaiko onto the bread

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:30.640
Bake for 3 more minutes and it is complete

